keywords={internet of things;multi-party computations;privacy;security;ubiquitous},
abstract={In this paper we consider different approaches to technological protection of users' privacy in the world of internet of things. Particularly, we consider what kind of problems and which level of protection can be achieved by applying approaches using secure multi-party computations.},
