abstract={With the advent of Internet of Things (IoT), information security issues will be a major bottleneck of the future development of IoT. How to resolve the information security problems of IoT effectively has become an important research issue. Firstly, various potential information security issues and preventive measures in the application of IoT are summarized. Then, the general architecture of trusted security system based on IoT is first proposed based on the former researches about trusted computing, trusted network, etc. Finally, according to the general architecture of trusted security system based on IoT, a study of concrete realization of trusted security system based on IoT is made, which mainly includes trusted user module, trusted perception module, trusted terminal module, trusted network module and trusted agent module.},
